name: London Women Who Go
body:
### Who Are We
We're a chapter of [Women Who Go](http://www.womenwhogo.org/), which was founded in San Francisco by Sarah Adams in May 2015. Sue Spence (@virtualsue) started this chapter in September 2015. If you identify as a woman, are interested in the Go programming language and can come to one of our meetings, you are most welcome to join us.

You can find us on [Meetup](http://www.meetup.com/Women-Who-Go-London/).
Twitter announcements: @womenwhogolndn.
